{"tid":949753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荷里活暖男明星包機  送陣亡美軍家屬遊迪士尼","createTime":"2018-12-21T04:39:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T14:53:21.000Z","uid":184679,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c409089e1e28cde845802c3e5b4018189dc58c4b","tid":949753,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T04:39:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_sweQX0bulYTKVhRfTdprQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzY4O2g9Njg3O2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/zh_hant_tw/News/afp/life0002b.170418162004.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F_sweQX0bulYTKVhRfTdprQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NzY4O2g9Njg3O2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh_hant_tw%2FNews%2Fafp%2Flife0002b.170418162004.jpg&h=56dcdec1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n曾在電影扮演越戰中尉的演員蓋瑞辛尼茲，為了幫助為國捐軀的美軍家屬走出傷痛，特別在耶誕節前夕，租下飛機，帶了1750名孩童跟家人，到佛州迪士尼度假，登機時不少民眾，向他們致敬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n12月的美國充滿濃厚的團聚氣氛，跟家人吃飯、收禮物是慶祝耶誕的方式之一，但有一群人過節時特別感傷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陣亡美軍家屬：「我們2011年在他生日時得知他陣亡，他4月時過世兩週年。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美軍在戰地不幸身亡，讓家人們到佳節時刻備感思念，這讓曾在電影阿甘正傳中扮演中尉的蓋瑞辛尼茲，感受特別深刻。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n旁白：「在2011年他(蓋瑞辛尼茲)創辦，蓋瑞辛尼茲基金會，每年募款3千萬美元，其中一個計畫是雪球特快。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n帶為國捐軀軍人的孩童去迪士尼玩的想法，其實是來自於一名士兵的遺願。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基金會影片旁白：「他(陣亡士兵)要求他的妻子，要對孩子兌現承諾，帶他們去迪士尼。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於是今年在田納西的納許維爾機場，基金會租多架飛機，載1750名罹難跟倖存者美軍的家屬飛到佛州迪士尼，登機前不少民眾向他們致敬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n旁白：「登機門附近的旅客暫停動作，並唱起國歌軍人也起立向他們致敬。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蓋瑞辛尼茲到機場為孩童送行， 希望這些家庭可透過活動認識彼此，進而獲得支持，為耶誕節創造新回憶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0e_AtgZv7L6LzyNzsUM91Q--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-TW/homerun/news_tvbs_com_tw_938/27a10be90a03fafded8d16d8acf4b395\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F0e_AtgZv7L6LzyNzsUM91Q--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-TW%2Fhomerun%2Fnews_tvbs_com_tw_938%2F27a10be90a03fafded8d16d8acf4b395&h=d1dd4e51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A5%BD%E8%90%8A%E5%A1%A2%E6%9A%96%E7%94%B7%E6%98%8E%E6%98%9F%E5%8C%85%E6%A9%9F-%E9%80%81%E9%99%A3%E4%BA%A1%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E9%81%8A%E8%BF%AA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%BC-094819881.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E8%2590%258A%25E5%25A1%25A2%25E6%259A%2596%25E7%2594%25B7%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2598%259F%25E5%258C%2585%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%2599%25A3%25E4%25BA%25A1%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25BB%258D%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25BF%25AA%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E5%25B0%25BC-094819881.html&d=MZBLinVCFmKnUYoufZkhYSwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=cc86a2c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A5%BD%E8%90%8A%E5%A1%A2%E6%9A%96%E7%94%B7%E6%98%8E%E6%98%9F%E5%8C%85%E6%A9%9F-%E9%80%81%E9%99%A3%E4%BA%A1%E7%BE%8E%E8%BB%8D%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E9%81%8A%E8%BF%AA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%BC-094819881.html</a>"},{"pid":"50b6fd293609b4610b7b17062231b78fea02ad1e","tid":949753,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T04:44:26.000Z","msg":"如果係腥港 又會畀人話借死人上位"},{"pid":"15fecd573625f267aaff5c3f123e47c5e8f49c30","tid":949753,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T04:45:50.000Z","msg":"條友借死人上位<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfefa778be01fc3738dfc0fb48ce5e1c9eb40b4","tid":949753,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T04:57:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f20feaedc541add409485649383b9f7da5aedefe","tid":949753,"uid":11092,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T06:00:31.000Z","msg":"lieutenant dan <img src=\"/assets/